m/note-4/general/emmc-bug-fix-tried-sm-n910g-sm-n910p-sm-t3468721/page4 |dead-url= no }}</ref>還有電池因過熱風險而被召回。<ref>{{Cite web |url= https://www.theverge.com/2017/8/16/16156934/galaxy-note-4-battery-recall-att-fedex |title= "為電信運營商AT＆T的一些客戶提供的保險替代手機中的Galaxy Note 4電池正被召回，因為過熱風險" |author=  |date= 2017-05-24 |publisher= The Verge |language= en |accessdate=  |quote=  |archive-date= 2017-12-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171207082007/https://www.theverge.com/2017/8/16/16156934/galaxy-note-4-battery-recall-att-fedex |dead-url= no }}</ref>

